{"tid":1863480,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港大生遭意大利取消遊學　港大拒絕資助","createTime":"2020-02-05T07:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T08:06:13.000Z","uid":91432,"like":126,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a927441748620f7539295033f73fd6978a4b64","tid":1863480,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5jy6Wn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5jy6Wn.jpg&h=ca42aa2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>&quot;本地學生＝二等公民<br />\n最近HKU熱話<br />\n香港大學為內地生提供住宿做Self-Quarantine<br />\n小弟原本去意大利Exchange<br />\n（全HKU得我一個）勿起我底Please<br />\n意大利間學校因為武漢肺炎<br />\n唔比宿舍鎖匙我 就算我比曬租<br />\n一開始要求我自己比錢租酒店隔離14日<br />\n最後仲取消埋Exchange<br />\n果邊學校/HKU都冇資助我隔離去做Exchange<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>點解班<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸仔</span>可以拎<span style=\"color: brown;\">HKU</span>錢做隔離<br />\n明明腥撚曬Email 比班<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸仔</span><br />\n班<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸仔</span>死都要落黎</strong></span></span><br />\n好心學下意大利佬<br />\n唔自己比錢做隔離<br />\n就取消佢學位或者直接Gap佢Sem啦屌&quot;</strong>"},{"pid":"b4457441d98bd70f041c069e1e3dffb0f1175f59","tid":1863480,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30695c4d0fd7eb487c503de89566a8cc84244b3a","tid":1863480,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afb729fa0819162c83c6e6ab2ed93895f3af559","tid":1863480,"uid":88743,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nHKU垃撚圾"},{"pid":"20ad476e3a92178b0309444b181aad9e9bddcd79","tid":1863480,"uid":194298,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"94後香港人係香港不嬲係三等公